===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/'slaɪd/}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪd|-aɪd]]
===Etymology===
Old English ''[[slīdan]]''

===Verb===
{{en-verb|slides|sliding|slid}}

====Transitive====
# To cause to move in continuous contact with a surface
#: ''He '''slid''' the boat across the grass.''

